data.description: GREAT PRIME PROPERTY in excellent location in beautiful Chicago suburbs. Renovated in 2013, this move in ready upgraded home is for just you!  Awesome open concept with nice layout with a combo L-Shaped Living Dining Room.  Tasteful wood laminate flooring on Main Level and in ALL Bedrooms.  Stylish vinyl tiled flooring compliments the EX-LARGE FINISHED FAMILY ROOM. 2 CERAMIC TILED BATHROOMS. BRAND NEW PROFESSIONAL STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES in wood laminate kitchen, which can ACCOMMODATED kitchen table and chairs. Completely fenced in yard. Entry/Exit doors on both sides of house with separate walk-out to backyard (suitable for entertaining) from Lower Level Laundry/Utility Room. 2 car detached garage. Yard also has a separate storage shed.  ASK YOUR REALTOR TO SET A SHOWING "TODAY" TO COME SEE YOUR NEW HOME!!
